				<h2>What is the general consensus here about "thanks" at the end of questions?</h2>
<p>According to <a href="https://meta.stackexchange.com/questions/2950/should-hi-thanks-taglines-and-salutations-be-removed-from-posts">this page on Meta Stack Overflow,</a> salutations, tag lines, thanks, etc. should be removed from posts. If I do that here, are my edits likely to be accepted? Is it okay if I remove those things from questions?</p>

