				<p><p>Conflicting issues:</p>

<ol>
<li><p>Edits to reduce clutter are good.</p></li>
<li><p>Many small edits at once to old posts bump current questions off the front page.</p></li>
</ol>

<p>Thus: removing "thanks" is good, but searching for posts with "Thanks" and editing 50 of them in a ten minute period   not good.</p>
</p><br>
